  "reference_number": "CHW0027",
  "remarks": "\nThe Russian Ministry of Defence 27th Scientific Centre is an involved person under the Chemical Weapons (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following grounds: (1) the Russian Ministry of Defence 27th Scientific Centre is a member of, associated with, or acting on behalf of or at the direction of an entity, namely the Radiological Chemical and Biological Defence Troops of the Ministry of Defence of the Russian Federation, which is or has been responsible for, engaging in, providing support for, or promoting prohibited activity related to chemical weapons. Specifically, the Russian Ministry of Defence 27th Scientific Centre is subordinate to the Radiological Chemical and Biological Defence Troops, which have been involved in the transfer and use of chemical weapons in Ukraine; (2) The Russian Ministry of Defence 27th Scientific Centre is or has been providing support for a prohibited activity related to chemical weapons.\n",
